        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>First Rhode Island Regiment Congressional Gold Medal Act</strong></p> <p>This bill provides for the award of a single Congressional Gold Medal to the First Rhode Island Regiment, collectively, in recognition of their dedicated service during the Revolutionary War.</p>]]></text>
